Speaker 1: Yes, I was told that my medication would be due here today, and I'm at the post office.

Speaker 2: And UPS hasn't shown or delivered anything, and I was wondering what the holdup might be.

Speaker 1: Yeah, I could take a look into that.

Speaker 2: Last name is Green, G-R-E-E-N-E, my first name is Dean, D-E-A-N.

Speaker 1: Well, they should make you jump through a bunch of hoops to get their money, and then they don't deliver.

Speaker 2: Well, if you deliver the package, I'll verify that, and I'm going to put you in a brief hold.
